								<ECUC-REFERENCE-DEF UUID="5467bf63-a327-4fdf-a15e-5566ad268841">
									<SHORT-NAME>vBRSVariantUsageOfvLinkGen</SHORT-NAME>
									<LONG-NAME>
										<L-4 L="EN">This executable: Use vLinkGen Variant</L-4>
									</LONG-NAME>
									<DESC>
										<L-2 L="EN">vLinkGenVariant reference for current executable.
The chosen variant will be generated into vBrsCfg.h and then be used in vLinkGen_Lcfg.c.
Furthermore, it will also be generated as BRS_LINKER_COMMAND_FILE_POSTFIX into Makefile.config.generated.
This will override the LINKER_COMMAND_FILE parameter in the Makefile. LINKER_COMMAND_FILE is used for the linkage target of the MakeSupport.

Note: /MICROSAR/vLinkGen/vLinkGenGeneral/vLinkGenFileGeneration shall be set to ONE_FILE_PER_VARIANT, in order to generate the corresponding link file for each variant.</L-2>
									</DESC>
