												<L-4 L="EN">Frequency is similar with timer peripheral clock</L-4>
											</LONG-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">If enabled, the clock defined in 
vBRSHwConfig/vBRSPeriphClock
will also be used for the peripheral clock, used by the LIN driver.

